'''克里斯蒂安·波特'''（{{lang-en|Christian Porter}}；{{bd|1970年|7月11日}}）是[[澳洲|澳洲]][[政治家|政治家]]，屬於[[澳洲自由黨|澳洲自由黨]]。他在2008年首次當選[[西澳州|西澳州]]立法會議員，2013年轉戰[[澳洲眾議院|聯邦眾議院]][[皮爾斯_(澳大利亞國會選區)|皮爾斯選區]]並當選。他在[[滕博爾內閣|滕博爾內閣]]擔任社會服務部長<ref name="reshuffle2014-3">{{cite news|title=Tony Abbott cabinet reshuffle moves Scott Morrison out of immigration|date=21 December 2014|accessdate=21 December 2014|url=http://www.theguardian.com/australia-news/2014/dec/21/tony-abbott-cabinet-reshuffle-moves-scott-morrison-out-of-immigration|author=Taylor, Lenore|work=[[Guardian_Australia|Guardian Australia]]|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112013943/http://www.theguardian.com/australia-news/2014/dec/21/tony-abbott-cabinet-reshuffle-moves-scott-morrison-out-of-immigration|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="sworn">{{cite news|title=Tony Abbott's revamped Ministry sworn in at Government House|url=http://www.news.com.au/national/tony-abbotts-revamped-ministry-sworn-in-at-government-house/story-fncynjr2-1227164880085|work=news.com.au|publisher=[[News_Corp_Australia|News Corp Australia]]|date=23 December 2014|accessdate=23 December 2014|archive-date=2015-09-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150914052514/http://www.news.com.au/national/tony-abbotts-revamped-ministry-sworn-in-at-government-house/story-fncynjr2-1227164880085|dead-url=no}}</ref>，2017年改任[[澳洲律政部長|澳洲律政部長]]及众议院领袖。在2021年[[第二屆莫里遜內閣|第二屆莫里遜內閣]]的改組中，他改任工業、科學與科技部長。

